@startuml state_machine
!theme plain
skinparam stateFontSize 12

title Raffle Entry Lifecycle - State Machine

[*] --> Inactive : Raffle created

state Inactive : isActive = false\nNo public interactions

state AcceptingEntries : isActive = true\ndrawnCount = 0\nSelf-registration open

state DrawingStarted : isActive = true\ndrawnCount > 0\nSelf-registration closed

Inactive --> AcceptingEntries : Admin activates\n(no prior draws)
AcceptingEntries --> DrawingStarted : First name drawn\n(POST /draw)
DrawingStarted --> AcceptingEntries : Admin resets draws\n(POST /reset)
AcceptingEntries --> Inactive : Admin deactivates
DrawingStarted --> Inactive : Admin deactivates

@enduml
